con:property.con:name: getETSAppoinmentId
con:property.con:value: SELECT BKNG_ID,ETS_APNTMT_ID,CUST_FST_NAM FROM BKNG WHERE BKNG_ID IN (SELECT DISTINCT BKNG.BKNG_ID FROM BKNG,TST,TST_VARTN WHERE BKNG.DLVY_MDE_CDE <> 'PBT' AND BKNG.BKNG_STS_TYP_CDE = 'RSRVD' AND TST.PGM_CDE = 'TEL' AND BKNG.TST_ID = TST.TST_ID AND TST_VARTN.TST_ID = BKNG.TST_ID MINUS SELECT TST_SCR_XML.BKNG_ID FROM TST_SCR_XML) AND DATE_CREATED IS NOT NULL AND CUST_FST_NAM LIKE 'slfirst%' ORDER BY DATE_CREATED DESC

con:property.con:name: addAccomodationPackage
con:property.con:value: Insert into CUST_ACMDTN_TST (CUSTOMER_ID,PGM_CDE,TST_ID,DLVY_MDE_CDE,ACMDTN_TYP_CDE,ACMDTN_TYP_VAL_ID_NO,APRVD_DTE,EXPRTN_DTE,OTHR_ACMDTN_TYP_TXT,CREATED_BY_ADMIN_USR_ID,CREATED_BY_CUSTOMER_ID,DATE_CREATED,UPDATED_BY_ADMIN_USR_ID,UPDATED_BY_CUSTOMER_ID,DATE_UPDATED) values (SELECT CREATED_BY_CUSTOMER_ID FROM BKNG WHERE BKNG_ID = ${Properties#BKNG_ID},'TEL',29,'CBT','92',null,to_date(SYSDATE,'DD-MON-RR'),to_date(SYSDATE + 365,'DD-MON-RR'),null,122,null,to_timestamp(SYSDATE,'DD-MON-RR HH.MI.SSXFF AM'),null,null,null)
